      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0656P0-01372'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0656P0_20040127_GCR_50' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Clause 40 agreed to.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0656P0-01373'>
