          <p class='first-para'>
            I was talking not about theft, but about the possibility of people attacking flasks in transit, and that sort of thing&#x2014;which they do. It is not a figment of my imagination. The 24 kilometres would almost certainly cover most of the distance that we are talking about, whereas the transhipment sites are often more than 5 kilometres away from the nuclear site. I want to make sure that the jurisdiction is wide enough to cover eventualities.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0656P0-01528'>
        <a name='S5LV0656P0_20040127_GCR_206'>  </a>
