            He referred to his anticipation that the range will be much the same as that available to other Home Office forces. I asked a question specifically about how their weaponry will compare with that of the MoD and I hope that in writing to me he will take that inquiry into consideration and provide the information.</p><p>
            It is the expectation and wish of all that training should be to a like standard as that of Home Office forces. Although throughout one is referring to lethal and less lethal weapons, less lethal weapons can sometimes, when deployed, also be lethal. Training is therefore important. I beg leave to withdraw the amendment.
