            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_133gc' title='Col. 133GC &mdash; HL Deb 27 January 2004 vol 656 c133GC' name='column_133gc' href='#column_133gc' rel='bookmark'>133GC</a>
            years. We believe that that is what will be incurred; that is the figure about which the assurances have been given. Costs relate to additional staff and members of the police authority. Those staff are needed to ensure that the whole process goes as smoothly and properly as can be achieved.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0656P0-01577'>
        <a name='S5LV0656P0_20040127_GCR_255'>  </a>
