      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0656P0-01579'>
        <a name='S5LV0656P0_20040127_GCR_257'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-joyce-anelay' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0656P0_20040127_GCR_257' title='Link to this speech by Ms Joyce Anelay' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/ms-joyce-anelay" title="Ms Joyce Anelay">Baroness Anelay of St Johns</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            I thank the noble Lord for that answer. The question had been put to me. I
            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_134gc' title='Col. 134GC &mdash; HL Deb 27 January 2004 vol 656 c134GC' name='column_134gc' href='#column_134gc' rel='bookmark'>134GC</a>
            shall consider carefully what the Minister has said. I appreciate the fact that the Government have tried to give reassurances on these matters, but they will be aware that uncertainty remains outwith this House with regard to that matter. I shall consult and have regard to any representations made to me before the Report stage. I beg leave to withdraw the amendment.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0656P0-01580'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0656P0_20040127_GCR_258' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Amendment, by leave, withdrawn.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0656P0-01581'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0656P0_20040127_GCR_259' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Clause 66 agreed to.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0656P0-01582'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0656P0_20040127_GCR_260' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Clauses 67 to 71 agreed to.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0656P0-01583'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0656P0_20040127_GCR_261' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Schedule 15 agreed to.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0656P0-01584'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0656P0_20040127_GCR_262' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Clauses 72 and 73 agreed to.
      </p>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0656P0-01585'>
        <a name='S5LV0656P0_20040127_GCR_263'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-david-triesman' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0656P0_20040127_GCR_263' title='Link to this speech by Mr David Triesman' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-david-triesman" title="Mr David Triesman">Lord Triesman</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            This might be a convenient moment for the Committee to adjourn until next Tuesday at 3.30 p.m.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0656P0-01586'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0656P0_20040127_GCR_264' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        The Committee adjourned at twelve minutes before eight o'clock.
      </p>
